settings.title: planet-friendly
settings.content: Gutsy uses insects as an outstanding source of protein. The ecological footprint of insects is 30 times smaller per kg than that of beef. This means that by serving Gutsy you and your dog have the opportunity to reduce your own carbon footprint as well.

settings.title: Locally produced
settings.content: To keep our pawprint as small as possible, we exclusively choose local products. All of Gutsy's ingredients are carefully chosen and come from within a 100-mile radius of where we make our delicious kibble.

settings.title: 100% recyclable
settings.content: Our packaging is made of mono-plastic, which means all bags are 100% recyclable. So please make sure to sort them after use!

settings.title: ridiculously tasty
settings.content: Spoil your dog with crunchy dog food full of flavor. Because your faithful companion only deserves the best.

settings.title: a surprising solution
settings.content: With our hybrid solution, using both insects and chicken, we make sustainable dog food sexy and accessible. Join the Gutsy pack on our adventure to change the world.

settings.title: Expert approved
settings.content: Thanks to our collaboration with accredited experts, we are able to serve fantastic kibble which taste deliciously and digest wonderfully.

settings.headline: HYPOALLERGENIC
settings.paragraph: Our kibble is hypoallergenic and therefore perfect for dogs with a sensitive stomach. Allergic reactions are a thing of the past, you can ask our loyal customer Otis!

settings.headline: HIGH QUALITY PROTEINS
settings.paragraph: Not all proteins are easy to digest. That is where Gutsy makes the difference. We only use high-quality and easy digestible proteins in our dog food.

settings.headline: AN ECOLOGICAL ALTERNATIVE
settings.paragraph: Thanks to our extraordinary ingredients such as insects, apples, carrots and beets, we ensure that your dog receives a healthy and well-balanced diet.

settings.headline: RICH IN VITAMINS & MINERALS
settings.paragraph:
Insects do not only have tiny legs, they also have a tiny ecological footprint, you can feed your dog with a clean conscience.

settings.headline: NATURAL CLEANERS
settings.paragraph: The favorite food of insects? Our leftovers! They feed themselves with leftover wheat and beet sugar. So no planet was harmed by feeding insects.

settings.testimonial_content: Quinn is crazy about Gutsy. She has never emptied her bowl so quickly. Best of all, she doesn't even realise that she is doing her part for the climate.
Nono is a proud mother of 4 fantastic puppies. With Gutsy, we have found a perfectly balanced diet for the whole family.
We had to search for a long time for the right food for Henry as he is allergic to all kinds of ingredients, but thanks to Gutsy's hypoallergenic dog food, these allergies are a thing of the past.
